384
00:17:17,550 --> 00:17:18,800
多谢了
Thank you!

385
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:20,070
这是个标牌  兄弟
It's a sign, bro.

386
00:17:23,330 --> 00:17:24,990
-有人犯心脏病了  -马修
- Heart attack! - Marshall!

387
00:17:25,130 --> 00:17:27,280
-马修  -泰德
- Marshall! Oh! - Ted! Ted!

388
00:17:29,990 --> 00:17:31,480
岁月啊
Time...

389
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:37,330
-莉莉  -莉莉
- Lily! - Lily!

390
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:41,610
马修  你发现了吗
Marshall, do you get what this means?

391
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:43,120
生命还没有太匆匆
Life isn't moving too fast.

392
00:17:43,120 --> 00:17:44,780
我们还来得及做任何事
We-we still have time for everything!

393
00:17:44,780 --> 00:17:46,870
我们也没有错过音乐会
And we're not gonna miss the concert!

