我的天  出什么事了
Oh, my God, what happened?

403
00:18:06,750 --> 00:18:09,540
我暂时不想谈这个  不过
I don't really feel like getting into it, but...

404
00:18:10,020 --> 00:18:11,760
我想我已经看见胜利的曙光了
I think the worst part is over.

405
00:18:18,300 --> 00:18:19,440
-凯文  -你好  凯文
- Hey, Kev. - What's up, Kev?

406
00:18:19,450 --> 00:18:20,150
还好吗  老兄
How's it going, buddy?

407
00:18:20,150 --> 00:18:21,210
各位好呀
Hey, guys.

408
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:23,360
有件事我必须告诉你
There's something I have to tell you.

409
00:18:23,860 --> 00:18:25,400
我不想听
Then don't.

410
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,530
什么
What?

