What do you think?

422
00:19:01,430 --> 00:19:04,290
我的生活一团糟
I'm such a mess.

423
00:19:06,740 --> 00:19:08,590
你为什么会喜欢我
Why do you even like me?

424
00:19:08,620 --> 00:19:09,650
过来
Come here.

425
00:19:11,330 --> 00:19:15,140
你说的每一件事都让我惊喜
I am constantly amazed by the things you say,

426
00:19:15,730 --> 00:19:18,070
